  },
  {
    appliance: 'LG Washer',
    location: 'Anaheim Hills',
    quote: "LG washer — LE error code, drum won't spin",
    description: 'Large home in Anaheim Hills with an LG front-loader showing LE error — motor overload fault. On inspection the direct drive motor stator had failed, a known failure point on LG units in this generation. Replaced the stator assembly with an OEM LG part. Ran three full cycles before leaving to confirm no recurrence. Customer had asked a neighbor about repair — that neighbor had been quoted a new washer by another company.',
    outcome: '✓ Same day · LG OEM direct drive stator assembly · 1.5 hours'
  },
  {
    appliance: 'GE Monogram Refrigerator',
    location: 'Anaheim Hills',
    quote: 'GE Monogram refrigerator — not cooling, compressor running constantly',
    description: "Built-in GE Monogram in a custom Anaheim Hills kitchen — running constantly but not reaching temperature. Thermistor had failed, causing the control board to misread the cabinet temperature and run the compressor indefinitely. Replaced the thermistor, cleared the error log, verified temperature stabilization over 45 minutes before leaving. Classic misdiagnosis opportunity — the compressor sounds fine, so many techs replace it unnecessarily. We don't.",
    outcome: '✓ Same day · GE Monogram OEM thermistor · 1.5 hours'
  },
  {
    appliance: 'Scotsman Ice Machine',
    location: 'Resort District',
    quote: 'Commercial ice machine — mold contamination, Disneyland area restaurant',
    description: "Restaurant near the resort area — Scotsman ice machine producing discolored ice with off smell. Full mold remediation: drained and sanitized the reservoir, replaced the water filter and distribution tube, cleaned all internal surfaces per manufacturer spec. Retested ice quality. This is exactly the kind of call where cutting corners has health consequences — we don't rush commercial food equipment jobs.",
