  },
  {
    question: 'Do you offer a warranty on repairs?',
    answer: 'All repairs include a 90-day warranty on parts and labor. If the same issue returns within 90 days, we come back and fix it at no charge. This is standard on every repair we do in Anaheim.'
  },
  {
