    answer: `Call ${branch.phone} — someone who knows our OC schedule picks up, not a call center. We'll give you a real arrival window. You can also book online at samedayappliance.repair. We're available Monday–Friday 7am–9pm, Saturday 8am–7pm, Sunday 9am–5pm.`
  },
